  m_text: "The morning begins in confusion. \nI wake up in a cold stone chamber with
    no memory of how I got here. \nThe air feels heavy, the silence louder than any
    scream. Something deep inside tells me this place isn\u2019t real... \nBut it
    feels painfully real."
